spec_data.Name: emacs-color-theme-el
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the elisp source files for Emacs Color Themes under GNU
Emacs. You do not need to install this package to run Emacs Color Themes.
Install the emacs-color-theme package to use Emacs Color Themes with GNU Emacs.
